sentences.english: You're pushing him and that's different than steering something that is going to cause death into another.
sentences.chinese: 你推他和因爲轉盤導致其他死亡是大不相同的。

sentences.english: Today's Shanghai is quite different from what it used to be .
sentences.chinese: 今天的止海與往昔大不相同了。

sentences.english: The other palaeogeographic units were also changed and were different from those in the previous ages.
sentences.chinese: 其他古地理單元也與以前各世的大不相同或有所不同。

sentences.english: Another factor was that men and women express emotional distress in different ways.
sentences.chinese: 另外，男人和女性表達悲痛的方式大不相同。

sentences.english: The heat of these irons was different from that used by housewives.
sentences.chinese: 這些熨斗跟家庭主婦們的熨牛大不相同。

sentences.english: The lithofacies palaeogeographic characteristics were quite different from those of the Cambrian.
sentences.chinese: 這與該地區寒武紀的巖相古地理格局大不相同。

sentences.english: As you can see, these fishing tools are very different.
sentences.chinese: 正如你所見到的，這些打撈工具是大不相同的。

sentences.english: However, the environment has changed dramatically since last October.
sentences.chinese: 但是，今天的環境，較諸去年十月已大不相同。

sentences.english: Her behavior has become exhibitionist and totally out of character.
sentences.chinese: 她的行爲變成愛出風頭，跟她正常的性格大不相同。

sentences.english: The appearance of these villages is quite different from what it used to be.
sentences.chinese: 這幾個村的村貌與以前大不相同。

sentences.english: Widely different was the effect of a second perusal.
sentences.chinese: 第二遍讀起來效果就大不相同了。

sentences.english: Fortunately, our ultracold atom clouds are very unlike ice cubes.
sentences.chinese: 幸運的是，我們的超冷原子雲和冰塊大不相同。

sentences.english: Drizzt returns to Luskan, and the Realms will never be the same!
sentences.chinese: 崔斯特回到路斯坎，諸國度將大不相同。

sentences.english: Even though John and David are twins, they are very different(from each other) in personality.
sentences.chinese: 雖然約翰和大衛是雙胞胎，他們在個性方面大不相同。

sentences.english: Running your own office equipment also makes a big difference.
sentences.chinese: 而開動自己的辦公設備就大不相同了。

sentences.english: Now I have a very different impression of Shanghai.
sentences.chinese: 如今我對上海的印象大不相同了。
